current_commit_message: Improved repr of SigmaString to avoid confusion with tuple
Added search variable to aggregation template in correlation queries
Added processing condition expressions to documentation
Mentioned base package name in docs.
Update test.yml with new OS versions and added Python 3.13
Added tests for conditions in post-processing items
Re-added CompareOperators to SigmaCompareExpression for backward-compatibility
Fixed MatchValueCondition: incopmpatible types result in false result
Reducing initialization of processing pipeline to once per conversion run.
Add from_yaml wrapper class method to SigmaCorrelationRule, SigmaFilter, and SigmaRule with specific return value type hint
Initialize conversion processing pipeline in convert_rule if it isn't defined yet.
Add callback support to convert and convert_rule
Enhance callback functionality in conversion methods to allow result modification
Changed release action runner to latest
